# Runtime/data artifacts. In a real install these live in the plugin DATA dir,
# never in the core. But running the scripts in-place (dev checkout, no plugin
# env) writes them under the skill dir — keep them out of the committed core.
skills/professor-synapse/.summon-state/
skills/professor-synapse/memory/
skills/professor-synapse/agents/INDEX.md.tmp

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.pyc
